01:08:50.794 --> 01:08:52.630
- Christopher?
- Ah.

01:08:52.712 --> 01:08:54.546
No, no. Don't get up.

01:08:55.548 --> 01:08:58.176
Is this your... your next masterpiece?

01:08:58.259 --> 01:08:59.510
Yes.

01:08:59.594 --> 01:09:02.930
The next great American novel.

01:09:05.350 --> 01:09:10.313
Of course, you and I both know I've only
written one good book my entire life.

01:09:11.106 --> 01:09:13.024
And I remember...

01:09:15.234 --> 01:09:18.488
I remember you
walking around with the manuscripts

01:09:18.571 --> 01:09:20.198
in a shopping bag all over the city.

01:09:20.281 --> 01:09:21.573
Huh?

01:09:21.658 --> 01:09:25.953
