01:09:41.720 --> 01:09:42.888
No...

01:09:49.103 --> 01:09:50.435
Can...

01:09:51.229 --> 01:09:52.731
you...

01:09:52.814 --> 01:09:54.942
come back to me?

01:11:53.559 --> 01:11:55.187
Full disclosure, Fenton:

01:11:55.770 --> 01:11:57.981
I never would have asked you
to come back to New York

01:11:58.065 --> 01:12:01.026
