about wanting to publish this novel.

01:12:01.109 --> 01:12:02.861
Yeah, soon, James...

01:12:04.238 --> 01:12:06.558
To be honest, I feel like
I've just hit on something and...

01:12:07.490 --> 01:12:10.160
you know, I'd like some more time,
if it's possible.

01:12:10.244 --> 01:12:12.162
Please keep writing.

01:12:33.851 --> 01:12:35.227
Layla.

01:12:36.061 --> 01:12:37.312
Layla!

01:12:38.146 --> 01:12:40.773
- I did not...
- You didn't knock.

01:12:40.858 --> 01:12:43.110
Layla, could you please
put some clothes on.

01:12:43.193 --> 01:12:44.777
Oh, come on, don't be such a prude.

01:12:44.862 --> 01:12:47.548
