Tell her to put some clothes on, John.

01:12:49.950 --> 01:12:51.910
- Layla, put some...
- The fuck, John?!

01:12:51.994 --> 01:12:53.287
Oh, shit. Sorry.

01:12:53.369 --> 01:12:55.454
