01:12:55.538 --> 01:12:56.915
Therapy.

01:12:57.707 --> 01:13:00.878
Oh, and to tell you Jessie's wedding
is in an hour, so...

01:13:00.961 --> 01:13:02.963
Hurry up or you're going to be late.

01:13:17.852 --> 01:13:19.980
Why are you walking so fast?

01:13:20.063 --> 01:13:22.232
Because it's important to me.

01:13:28.030 --> 01:13:31.866
So, you know I have to go back to Bard
in a couple of days, right?

01:13:31.950 --> 01:13:35.078
Yeah, funny thing about that actually...

01:13:36.246 --> 01:13:37.538
Yeah, what's that?

01:13:37.622 --> 01:13:40.375
